 8:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517000' id='t-517000'>There have been many other exhibitions in the meantime,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521000' id='t-521000'>but I don't want to focus on my shows.</span>
