<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1007000' id='t-1007000'>in this particular kind of delivery.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1009000' id='t-1009000'>Similarly, there's the work of people like Marti Guixe that tries to involve</span>
